API SIMULATION - JSON SERVER

It's necessary to have a json server to simulate a API without using existing one with limitations

Install JSON SERVER by using NPM manager : npm i json-server

Creation of a DB as json file in a data folder

Give the command "server" : "json-server --watch data/db.json" in the package.json script

run npm run server command

